  • Method Details

    • getPropertyRecords

      public static List<PropertyRecord> getPropertyRecords()
      Provides read-only access to the entire list of PropertyRecord objects loaded from the CSV. If the CSV was never read or an error occurred, this might be null or an empty list. Callers must not modify this list in place.
      Returns:
      the loaded list of PropertyRecord objects, or null if not yet assigned
